Neoma Judge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoma_Judge 0 Naoma Judge (September 27, 1908 in Mitchell, South Dakota, USA. - June 7, 1978 in Daly City, California, USA.) was an actress of the 1930s.Judge was of the WAMPAS Baby Stars selected by the Western Association of Motion Picture Advertisers in 1934.
